name: ꗨ5-3
description: In 2019, Philadelphia's 5th Street subway station underwent renovations that briefly exposed pillars with historic numeral 5s painted on them. Only weeks after they were revealed, the 5s were painted over and the renovations continued. ꗨ5 is a series inspired by transience and shared space. Each piece in this series depicts a painted 5 that briefly made the world more interesting. Each digital piece, in large format print resolution is an edition of 5.
